---
layout: base
---

<section class="banner">
  <div class="fifty --threshold-0 --gap-3 maxw-5">
    <aside class="flex --column --gap-none --start">
      <span class="size-1 bold text-primary italic lowercase">&lt;web-tinkerer /&gt;</span>
      <h1>Kevin Pennekamp</h1>
      <p class="mt-000 maxw-3">I am a Dutch software engineer, specialised in the web platform as a whole. In particular <span class="flag">CSS</span>.  I enjoy <a href="/writing">writing</a> about all the exciting new stuff I encounter about the web and software development. This is my digital playground & corner of the internet.</p> 
    </aside>
    <div class="flex --column">
      {% include "svg/profile.svg" %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="banner" data-variant="colored">
  {% include "svg/line.svg" %}
  <div class="maxw-5 sidebar --left --threshold-0">
    <div></div>
    <div class="flex --column --gap-1 --stretch">
      <section class="info-section | sidebar --left --gap-000">
        <span class="bold text-primary">What.</span>
        <div class="flex --column --gap-000 --start">
          <p>I specialize in development and consultancy on CSS, HTML, and sustainable web development. I mostly do this by using tools like Eleventy and Svelte. You can also ask me to help with mentoring and code-reviewing, if you are a (junior) indepedent developers.</p>
          <p>In the mean time, i I build my own stuff like <a href="https://feo.crinkles.dev" alt="FEO.css site">Feo.css</a>, and I <a href="/writing">write</a> (sometimes).</p>
        </div>
      </section> 
      <section class="info-section | sidebar --left --gap-000">
        <span class="bold text-primary">Work.</span>
        <p>I work for Finaps a (small-ish) software agency based in Amsterdam, the Nethelands. Here I lead a team of ~15 software engineers.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<main class="center --threshold-5 | mb-4">
  <div class="sidebar --right --threshold-0 --gap-5 | --start">
    <div class="flex --column --gap-00">
      <h2 class="size-0 text-2 uppercase">Here's my most recent posts</h2>
      {% set posts =  collections.posts | head(3) %}
      {% include "components/post-list.njk" %}
    </div>
    <aside class="flex --column --gap-000" aria-label="Top tags on the site">
      <span class="text-2">Filter by tag..</span>
      {% set tags = collections.posts | getAllTags %}
      {% include "components/tag-list.njk" %}
    </aside>
  </div>
</main>
